<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Review Submitted - <%= company_name %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Admin Container - matching admin design system */
    .admin-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .admin-container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .admin-container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #9a3412;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .admin-container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .admin-container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .content-section ul {
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .content-section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    /* Review Details Card */
    .review-details {
      background-color: #fef3c7;
      border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .review-details h3 {
      color: #92400e;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .review-details p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #b45309;
    }
    
    .review-details strong {
      color: #92400e;
    }
    
    .review-content {
      background-color: #fffbeb;
      border: 1px solid #fbbf24;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    
    .review-content p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #b45309;
    }
    
    .rating-display {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    
    .stars {
      color: #fbbf24;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .rating-text {
      color: #b45309;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    /* Admin Action Buttons */
    .admin-actions {
      background-color: #f0f9ff;
      border: 1px solid #60a5fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .admin-actions h3 {
      color: #1e40af;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ea580c;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      margin-right: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #dc2626;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #6b7280;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      margin-right: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-secondary:hover {
      background-color: #374151;
    }
    
    .next-steps {
      background-color: #f0fdf4;
      border: 1px solid #22c55e;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .next-steps h3 {
      color: #15803d;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .next-steps ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .next-steps li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #166534;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #ea580c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .verified-badge {
      background-color: #d1fae5;
      color: #065f46;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    
    .unverified-badge {
      background-color: #fee2e2;
      color: #dc2626;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="admin-container">
      <div class="admin-container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">üç™ <%= company_name %></div>
        <h1 class="admin-container-title">New Review Submitted</h1>
        <p class="admin-container-subtitle">A customer has shared their experience with your cookies</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <p>Hello Admin,</p>
          
          <p>Great news! A customer has just submitted a review for <%= company_name %> cookies. Here are the details:</p>
          
          <div class="review-details">
            <h3>üìù Review Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Customer:</strong> <%= @review.customer_display_name %></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @review.email %></p>
            <div class="rating-display">
              <strong>Rating:</strong>
              <span class="stars"><%= '‚òÖ' * @review.rating %><%= '‚òÜ' * (5 - @review.rating) %></span>
              <span class="rating-text"><%= @review.rating %>/5 stars</span>
            </div>
            <% if @review.title.present? %>
              <p><strong>Title:</strong> "<%= @review.title %>"</p>
            <% end %>
            <% if @review.verified_purchase? %>
              <p><strong>Purchase Status:</strong> 
                <span class="verified-badge">Verified Purchase</span>
                (Order #<%= @review.order.id %>)
              </p>
            <% else %>
              <p><strong>Purchase Status:</strong> 
                <span class="unverified-badge">Unverified</span>
              </p>
            <% end %>
            <p><strong>Submitted:</strong> <%= @review.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
            
            <% if @review.content.present? %>
              <div class="review-content">
                <p>"<%= @review.content %>"</p>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          
          <div class="admin-actions">
            <h3>üõ†Ô∏è Quick Actions</h3>
            <a href="<%= admin_review_url(@review) %>" class="admin-btn-primary">View in Admin Panel</a>
            <a href="<%= approve_admin_review_url(@review) %>" class="admin-btn-primary">Quick Approve</a>
            <a href="<%= admin_reviews_url %>" class="admin-btn-secondary">All Reviews</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>üìã Recommended Next Steps</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Review the content for appropriateness and authenticity</li>
              <li>Approve the review to make it visible to customers</li>
              <li>Consider featuring high-quality reviews on your homepage</li>
              <li>Respond to any concerns or questions if needed</li>
              <li>Thank the customer for their feedback</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <p>Customer reviews are valuable social proof that help build trust with potential customers. Take action on this review to maintain your excellent reputation!</p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>Happy reviewing!</p>
            <p class="signature-name">Your <%= company_name %> Review System</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>This is an automated notification from your <%= company_name %> review system.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            &copy; <%= Date.current.year %> <%= company_name %>. All rights reserved.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 